# Coordinator — Personal Cost Optimization Mode

For **personal Cursor account** coordinator sessions on Home Pantry. Full docs: [ENGINEERING_INTELLIGENCE.md](../../private/ENGINEERING_INTELLIGENCE.md#personal-cost-optimization-mode) · [SPAWN_BUDGET.md](../../private/SPAWN_BUDGET.md) · [AI_VALUE_DASHBOARD.md](../../private/AI_VALUE_DASHBOARD.md).

> **Core principle:** *Shipped value per dollar, not agent activity.*

**Hard guardrail:** On-Demand **$150–200/week**. Flag >**$200** without prod merge → pause explore/shell; max 1 feature-agent.

## 10 priorities (operational)

1. **Value per dollar** — track merged/deployed features, not agent count.
2. **Finish before starting** — merge/deploy open work before new P1 spawn.
3. **WIP caps** — 3 impl · 1 planner · 1 integration · 1 dev-runtime · 1 governance.
4. **One hot zone = one agent** — i18n, settings, `di.ts`, migrations, `hooks.server.ts`.
5. **Spawn proposal mandatory** — outcome · P0/P1/P2 · stop condition · S/M/L/XL · why not existing agent ([SPAWN_BUDGET](../../private/SPAWN_BUDGET.md)).
6. **Coordinator-only spawn** — no proposal → no spawn (except dev-runtime + single P0 fix when CI/prod red).
7. **Cost bands + XL gate** — split XL unless P0/P1 value + WIP clear + no hot-zone collision.
8. **Model policy** — default `auto`; `composer-2.5-fast` single bounded slice only.
9. **Cadence** — E2E: one batch/week after feature-freeze. Docs/intelligence: Monday only.
10. **Weekly rollup** — CSV → AI_COST → [AI_VALUE_DASHBOARD](../../private/AI_VALUE_DASHBOARD.md) + SPAWN_BUDGET.

Also applies: [coordinator-spawn-budget.mdc](./coordinator-spawn-budget.mdc) · [coordinator-v2.mdc](./coordinator-v2.mdc).
